# pdf-stamper

PDF stamper application which let you to add stamp on PDF document with your credentials.

How to use:
1. Run 'Application' class
2. Send request
3. You will get a response with PDF in base64 format




Example request body:
{
    "fileBytes": "",
    "imageBytes": "",
    "purpose": "Signing",
    "name": "Vardas_2 Pavard_2",
    "position": "Manager",
    "company": "UAB \"Company\"",
    "date": "2022-02-02",
    "textFont": {
        "name": "Verdana",
        "style": "0",
        "color": "black"
    },
    "renderingMode": "TRANSPARENT",
    "stampPosition": "TOP_LEFT"
}
